## Data access rules

- Query the `{{ gov_database }}` database. Allowed schemas (convention): {{ schema_allow | join(', ') }}.
- **Never** reference these schemas in committed app code: {{ schema_deny | join(', ') }}. This denylist is **auto-enforced**.
